"                        &lt;a href=\"#\" data-oe-nodeid=\"15\" "
"class=\"o_no_link_popover d-block o_knowledge_toc_link "
"o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_2\"&gt;🔄 ​Automatic replenishment&lt;/a&gt;\n"
"                        &lt;a href=\"#\" data-oe-nodeid=\"16\" "
"class=\"o_no_link_popover d-block o_knowledge_toc_link "
"o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_3\"&gt;Demo: automize the replenishment of the "
"game \"Pandemic\"&lt;/a&gt;\n"
"                        &lt;a href=\"#\" data-oe-nodeid=\"17\" "
"class=\"o_no_link_popover d-block o_knowledge_toc_link "
"o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_2\"&gt;🚚 ​Receive products from a purchase "
